      "role": "user",
      "content": "honestly yeah i think it's definitely just the stress. i've been on edge all day and i'm just super anxious about my connecting flight. you think doing some breathing exercises and maybe taking some herbal calming tea would be enough to get me through the next few hours? i really dont want to deal with a hospital in a foreign country if i dont have to.",
