      "content": "Breathing exercises and herbal calming tea can definitely help calm your nerves and manage anxiety. Try practicing some deep, slow breaths in through your nose and out through your mouth, and see if the herbal tea such as chamomile or peppermint helps to relax you. Additionally, you can also try some stress-reducing mental techniques like progressive muscle relaxation or visualization to help calm your mind. Consider visiting a nearby café or lounge with a mall or a quiet area where you can sit and catch your breath without being too overtly stressed.",
